{"data":{"post":{"html":"<p> <br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\nI recently came across that beautiful, evocative quote from Virginia Woolf's <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Waves\"><em>The Waves</em></a>. It reminded me of John Adams' <a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/music/tomserviceblog/2014/mar/11/symphony-guide-john-adams-harmonielehre-tom-service\"><em>Harmonielehre</em></a>, which perfectly captures the feeling of this, particularly in the last movement:\n <br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n  </p>\n<div style=\"position:relative;padding-bottom:56.25%;padding-top:30px;height:0;overflow:hidden;\">\n  <iframe style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/3X-IUE_muQA\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</div>\n<p> <br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\nJohn Adams is one of my favourite composers, and this quote is a great starting point for exploring his music. <em>Harmonielehre</em> is a fantastic, surreal, modern piece—you can read more about it in John Adams' own <a href=\"https://www.earbox.com/harmonielehre/\">piece description</a>.\n <br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n  </p>","frontmatter":{"title":"John Adams and Virginia Woolf","image":"blog/john-adams-virginia-woolf.jpg","description":"\"There was a star riding through clouds one night, & I said to the star, 'Consume me'.\"","date":"2019-02-27"}},"previous":null,"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/blog/synesthesia/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Synesthesia!"}},"image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":0.9383846794338052,"src":"/static/e52322be32c20a45c4ddc1557b777124/8484e/john-adams-virginia-woolf.jpg","srcSet":"/static/e52322be32c20a45c4ddc1557b777124/6ad16/john-adams-virginia-woolf.jpg 200w,\n/static/e52322be32c20a45c4ddc1557b777124/8f1ca/john-adams-virginia-woolf.jpg 400w,\n/static/e52322be32c20a45c4ddc1557b777124/8484e/john-adams-virginia-woolf.jpg 800w,\n/static/e52322be32c20a45c4ddc1557b777124/78809/john-adams-virginia-woolf.jpg 1127w","sizes":"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"}}}},"pageContext":{"post_slug":"/blog/john-adams-virginia-woolf/","img_path":"blog/john-adams-virginia-woolf.jpg","prev_slug":null,"next_slug":"/blog/synesthesia/"}}